ZH: 他是个见利忘义的人，只顾自己的利益而忘记了道义。
EN: He is a person who only cares about his own interests and forgets about morals.

ZH: 这种见利忘义的行为是不道德的。
EN: This kind of behavior that forsakes principles for profit is immoral.

ZH: 我们不能容忍见利忘义的行为。
EN: We cannot tolerate behavior that puts profit above principles.

ZH: 这种见利忘义的态度会给团队带来负面影响。
EN: This profit-driven attitude will bring negative impact to the team.

ZH: 他因为见利忘义而失去了许多朋友。
EN: He lost many friends because of his disregard for ethics in pursuit of profits.

ZH: 让我们共同抵制见利忘义的行为。
EN: Let's unite to resist behavior that puts profits above principles.

ZH: 良好的品德比见利忘义更重要。
EN: Good moral character is more important than sacrificing principles for profit.

ZH: 见利忘义将使一个人失去尊重。
EN: Putting profit above principles will make a person lose respect.

ZH: 认真对待道德准则，不要见利忘义。
EN: Take moral principles seriously and do not forsake them for profit.

ZH: 我们要坚决反对见利忘义的行为。
EN: We must firmly oppose behavior that values profit over ethics.

ZH: 他的见利忘义让所有人都感到失望。
EN: His pursuit of profit at the expense of ethics disappointed everyone.

ZH: 如果见利忘义成为一种风气，社会将变得混乱。
EN: If putting profit above principles becomes a trend, society will become chaotic.

ZH: 这个组织不能容忍任何见利忘义的成员。
EN: This organization cannot tolerate any members who disregard ethics for profit.

ZH: 必须要制止见利忘义的行为，才能维护社会稳定。
EN: We must stop behavior that prioritizes profit over ethics in order to maintain social stability.

ZH: 在商业界，见利忘义的行为时有发生。
EN: In the business world, behavior that disregards ethics for profit is common.

ZH: 当一个人开始见利忘义，他就会逐渐失去原则。
EN: When a person starts putting profit above principles, he will gradually lose integrity.

ZH: 我们应该在家庭教育中注重引导孩子不要见利忘义。
EN: We should guide children in family education to not forsake principles for profit.

ZH: 不管在任何情况下，见利忘义都是不应该的。
EN: Regardless of the situation, putting profit above principles is unacceptable.

ZH: 希望大家能自觉抵制见利忘义的行为。
EN: I hope everyone can consciously resist behavior that sacrifices principles for profit.

ZH: 在这个团队里，绝对不能允许任何见利忘义的成员存在。
EN: In this team, we cannot allow any members who prioritize profit over principles.
